ASK_USER=request_user_input
ASK_USER_OTHER_NOTE=explicitly in options
SKILLS_DIR=~/.codex/skills
RULES_SOURCE=`AGENTS.md` files in repo scope (root + nested)
DISPATCH_AGENT=Enable multi-agent tools (spawn_agent, wait, close_agent). Launch subagents in parallel, wait for all results. Use send_input for follow-ups if needed.
INVOKE_SKILL=Suggest the user run the target command manually.
PROGRESS_TOOL=
FILE_DISCOVERY=For file discovery, use available search tools. Do not fall back to shell commands unless no dedicated tool is available.
WEB_RESEARCH=For web research use available web search or fetch tools if available. If no web tools exist, ask the user to provide the needed information.
DISPATCH_RESEARCHER=Spawn a research subagent (spawn_agent) with the researcher prompt from this skill, wait for results.